<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="5Oct1933"><font color="red">5 October 1933</font> <i>NLSP</i> (from Carolus Verhulst of the Servire Press to Paul L&eacute;on): Thank you for your letter of October 3rd. We understand from it, that the text, as published in Transition, is the final one &hellip; We certainly shall bring the book out and it will certainly be before May 31st next. </div>
